comments: James (LAL) makes marginal contact to Green's (GSW) side on his driving shot attempt.
Wiggins (GSW) and Davis (LAL) engage and disengage as they pursue the loose ball.
James (LAL) gathers the ball on his left foot and hops consecutively on it.
Davis (LAL) extends his arm and brushes Curry's (GSW) arm at the end of his drive as he releases his pass.
Poole (GSW) establishes himself in Schroder's (LAL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Curry (GSW) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes his first step on his left, followed by his second step on his right and releases the pass prior to bringing his left foot back down.
Russell (LAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Wiggins (GSW) moves along Russell's (LAL) path and absorbs the marginal body contact contesting his shot attempt at the basket.
Schroder (LAL) brushes Curry's (GSW) shoulder in transition and he is able to move through the marginal contact.
Russell (LAL) makes marginal contact to Curry's (GSW) front during his dribble.
Poole (GSW) establishes himself in Schroder's (LAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Curry (GSW) attempts to bring the ball behind his back and the ball lightly skims Curry's leg as he continues his dribble.
Russell (LAL) initiates marginal contact with Curry's (GSW) off arm as Davis cleanly blocks the shot.
Poole (GSW) initiates contact with James' (LAL) arm after his gather and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) briefly grasps and then quickly releases Poole's (GSW) jersey as the pick is set.
Schroder (LAL) briefly places his hand Curry's (GSW) arm off ball and slides his hand off as he deflects the pass attempt.
Vanderbilt (LAL) immediately slides his hand off of Wiggins's (GSW) side and marginal contact occurs during the pick.

James (LAL) has his forearm slightly extended away from his body as marginal contact takes place to Poole's (GSW) side on his driving shot attempt.  Marginal contact occurs with Davis (LAL) as Poole's momentum carries him forward into his body.
Green (GSW) places his hand momentarily to Davis' (LAL) side as the drive to the basket is taking place.
Schroder (LAL) and Thompson (GSW) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Green (GSW) is actively guarding an opponent within three seconds of entering the lane.
Thompson (GSW) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with James' (LAL) arm.
Green (GSW) places his arms against Davis' (LAL) body and marginal contact occurs as Green slides his arms off in pursuit of the long rebound.
Wiggins (GSW) briefly grasps Vanderbilt's (LAL) arm as they come together underneath the basket before correcting.
Thompson (GSW) wraps his arm around and makes contact with Schroeder's (LAL) arm which affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs prior to the timeout being called.
Davis (LAL) briefly grasps DiVincenzo's (GSW) arm and immediately disengages as he moves through the marginal contact.
Thompson (LAL) establishes himself in DiVincenzo's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs to DiVincenzo's side as they disengage.
DiVincenzo (GSW) commits a take foul on Schroder (LAL).
Schroder (LAL) and Green (GSW) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Schroder (LAL) contest Green's (GSW) jump shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs after his release.
